# Robux Tax Calculator Ultimate 💎

This is a **fully featured Robux Tax Calculator** website, ready to deploy on GitHub Pages. Features:

- Live Robux → USD calculation  
- Custom DevEx rates  
- Robux Tier bonuses  
- Multiple currencies (USD, EUR, GBP)  
- Dark/Light mode toggle  
- Copy payout button  
- Animated chart showing Tax vs Payout  
- Fully responsive design  

## How to Deploy

1. Clone this repository:
